b"This Christmas, we\xe2\x80\x99re donating \xc2\xa32 million to good causes chosen by the nine world-famous icons voicing our festive videos.

This week's icon, Jeremy Irons, chose @icrrofficial and @the_hope_foundation to receive our \xc2\xa3100,000 donation. 

@the_hope_foundation works tirelessly with some of the most vulnerable children in society to provide protection, education and healthcare via over 60 projects including 11 protection homes. Our Christmas donation will go towards feeding the children in some of HOPE's protection homes in Kolkata, and will truly make a huge difference during such uncertain times. 

@icrrofficial are committed to providing emergency medical care to those seriously ill or injured in Ireland through the provision of a network of Volunteer Doctors, Rapid Response Vehicles and a dedicated Helicopter Emergency Medical Service. This donation will help protect communities, families and loved ones this Christmas."
